w.theverge.com/2024/11/14/24296777/tesla-catl-ev-battery-maker-elon-musk-4860-cell</id><author><name>奥马尔·沙基尔</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-11-14T18:33:11-05:00</published><updated> 2024-11-14T18:33:11-05:00</updated><title>您现在可以购买的最好的即时相机</title><content type="html">&lt;图>; &lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src =“https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/uLwBnCI-VbdGdcrxgmSG_CrADWo=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cd n.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/71015667/236751_Instant_Camera_Buying_Guide.7.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Kristen Radtke / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;我们找到了最适合您的预算和需求的相机。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https:// www.theverge.com/23133103/best-instant-cameras-fujifilm-polroid-kodak&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23133103/best-instant-cameras-fujifilm-polaroid-kodak" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23133103/best-instant-cameras-fujifilm-polroid-kodak</id><author><name>希娜·瓦萨尼</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-11-14T17:21:11-05:00</published><updated> 2024-11-14T17:21:11-05:00</updated><title> NASA 的人工智能地球副驾驶将回答您有关我们星球的问题</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;来自国际空间站的伊斯帕尼奥拉岛照片&quot; src =“https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/KP3j-NmsICSWzDxNmv1hfm-3aaw=/0x0:720x480/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73724012/nasa_satellite_view.0。 .jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;图片：&lt;a class=&quot;ql-link&quot; href=&quot;https://visibleearth.nasa.gov/images/152431/reflecting-on-hispaniola&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;NASA&lt;/a>;&lt;/ Figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;zokK89&quot;>;NASA 是 &lt;a href=&quot;https://blogs.microsoft.com/blog/2024/11/14/from-questions-to-discoveries-nasas-new-earth-copilot-brings-microsoft-ai-capability-to-democratize-access -to-complex-data/&quot;>;与 Microsoft 合作&lt;/a>;创建人工智能聊天机器人，旨在让您更轻松地访问和理解有关地球的科学数据。该工具名为 Earth Copilot，它将能够通过将 NASA 广泛的地理空间信息压缩为易于理解的响应来回答有关我们星球的问题。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;HlFPp6&quot;>;为了创建该工具，NASA正在将人工智能集成到其数据存储库中，允许 Earth Copilot 在回答问题时参考这些信息，例如“伊恩飓风对萨尼贝尔岛的影响是什么？”或“COVID-19 大流行如何影响美国的空气质量？”&lt;/p>; &lt;div id=&quot;Kv1YPK&quot;>;&lt;div style=&quot;left: 0; width: 100%; height: 0;position:relative ; padding-bottom: 56.25%;&quot;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;zJdAX6&quot;>;NASA 旨在通过推出 Earth Copilot 实现科学数据的“民主化”获取和理解NASA 内的信息...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/14/24296758/nasa-ai-earth-copilot-microsoft&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip ;&lt;/a>;&lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/14/24296758/nasa-ai-earth-copilot-microsoft" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/14/24296758/nasa-ai-earth-copilot-microsoft</id><author><name>艾玛·罗斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-11-14T17:13:50-05:00</published><updated> 2024-11-14T17:13:50-05:00</updated><title> Pokémon TCG Pocket 将从明年初开始让你交易卡牌</title><content type="html">&lt;图>; &lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src =“https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/-SrKDWOoDGu4ksUSj6JvQ1LHKS4=/227x0:2627x1600/1310x873/cd n.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73724006/Screen_Shot_2024_09_18_at_2.07.32_PM.0.png&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;口袋妖怪公司&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;9lHQk4&quot;>;&lt;em>;口袋妖怪集换式卡牌游戏口袋&lt;/em>;自&lt;a href=&quot;https: //www.theverge.com/2024/10/30/24283488/pokemon-tcg-pocket-is-finally-here&quot;>;上个月在全球范围内推出&lt;/a>;，其背后的团队分享了一些即将到来的更新的简短路线图 - 包括与其他人交换卡牌的能力。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;K8ze4o&quot;>;“我们的目标是添加一项功能，允许某些卡牌将于 2025 年 1 月开始交易”，根据团队的最新消息 &lt;a href=&quot;https://community.pokemon.com/en-us/discussion/14369/letter-to-the-community-nov-13-2024/&quot;>;官方神奇宝贝论坛&lt;/a>;。 “我们计划逐步扩大可交易卡牌的选择范围。”目前尚不清楚哪些卡牌最初可用于交易，希望列表的扩展不会花费太长时间。&lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id= &quot;7E3GC6&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{&quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Pokémon TCG Pocket 希望成为数字卡的门户正在收集&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/19/24248306/pokemon-tcg-pocket-hands-on&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt; /div>; &lt;p id=&quot;mrdHQT&quot;>;该游戏还将在今年年底前获得新的补充包。除了交易之外，还有其他新功能正在开发中......&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/14/24296690/pokemon-tcg -pocket-trade-cards&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/14/24296690/pokemon-tcg-pocket-trade-cards" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/14/24296690/pokemon-tcg-pocket-trade-cards</id><author><name>杰·彼得斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-11-14T16:35:40-05:00</published><updated> 2024-11-14T16:35:40-05:00</updated><title> Teenage Engineering 的新 OP–XY 让我希望自己有更多的音乐装备预算</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;白色背景下的青少年工程 OP-XY。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/ryr3Xx3C8BLmPds5t7-hFORYVyo=/0x0:3588x2392/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73723954/teenageengineering1.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;Teenage Engineering OP-XY 感觉像是该公司已有六年历史的 OP-Z 的升级版。&lt;/em>; |图片：青少年工程&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;RSMnyr&quot;>;青少年工程的新&lt;a href=&quot;https://teenage.engineering/products/op-xy&quot;>;OP-XY&lt;/a>;是一款便携式合成器和音序器，看起来类似于该公司的&lt;a href=&quot;https://teenage.engineering/store/op-1-field/?srsltid=AfmBOooacg__9SKptrN6z36SqsSz2iNnGPNsQv​​YrQey68CAe6jb1ASaq&quot;>;OP–1 字段&lt;/a>;。但从功能上来说，它是对公司&lt;a href=&quot;https://teenage.engineering/products/op-z&quot;>;已有六年历史的 OP-Z&lt;/a>; 的更强大的升级，更加注重分层具有各种效果的声音和 2,299 美元的更高价格标签。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;I4ZsJZ&quot;>;OP-XY 具有“阳极氧化、全黑表面”，是 Teenage 的另一个令人愉快的例子工程设计印章。它的黑白主题强调贯穿其 16 个音序器输入的灰度渐变，这与 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24191461/playdate-ereader-app-playbook-panic-teenage-工程&quot;>;亮黄色 Playdate 手持设备&lt;/a>;，由 Teenage Engineering 帮助 Panic 设计。与 429 美元的 OP-Z 依靠智能手机等移动设备作为屏幕不同，OP-XY 现在有黑色和...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge .com/2024/11/14/24296629/teenage-engineering-op-xy-instrument-synthesizer&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/14/24296629/teenage-engineering-op-xy-instrument-synthesizer" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/14/24296629/teenage-engineering-op-xy-instrument-synthesizer</id><author><name>安德鲁·利泽夫斯基</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-11-14T15:50:45-05:00</published><updated> 2024-11-14T15:50:45-05:00</updated><title> TikTok 将 Getty Images 插入其人工智能生成的广告和头像中</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;TikTok 徽标的矢量艺术。&quot; src =“https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/ZVodkScKVxTqVABgXF35o3lud1k=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x8 73/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73723835/STK051_TIKTOK_CVirginia_C.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;OHfva2&quot;>;TikTok 将让广告商&lt;a href=&quot;https://newsroom.gettyimages.com/en/getty-images/ getty-images-unlocks-premium-creative-content-for-tiktok-advertisers&quot;>;使用平台的人工智能广告制作工具时从 Getty Images 提取内容&lt;/a>;。通过集成，广告商可以使用 Getty 的许可图像和视频来制作包含人工智能生成内容的广告，包括看起来像真人的人工智能头像。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;Gjx6ND&quot;>;集成将通过 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/6/17/24179971/tiktok-ads-ai- generated-avatars-creators-language-dubbing&quot;>;TikTok 的 Symphony Creative Studio&lt;/a>; — 一个 AI-动力视频生成工具&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/14/24296429/more-ai- generated-ads-are-coming-to-tiktok&quot;>;今天向所有广告客户推出&lt;/a>;。该工具可以根据产品描述生成视频，添加人工智能头像来“谈论”产品，甚至可以采用不同语言的人工智能配音。广告商还可以使用该工具生成广告的多个版本，以及“重新混合”现有广告。&lt;/p>; &lt;figure class=&quot;e-image&quot;>; &lt;cite>;GIF：TikTok&lt;/cite>; &lt;figcaption >;&lt;em>;T...&lt;/em>;&lt;/figcaption>;&lt;/figure>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/14/24296636/tiktok-ai-ads-getty-images-content&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/14/24296636/tiktok-ai-ads-getty-images-content" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/14/24296636/tiktok-ai-ads-getty-images-content</id><author><name>艾玛·罗斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-11-14T15:31:45-05:00</published><updated> 2024-11-14T15:31:45-05:00</updated><title>购买 Garmin Fenix 7S Pro 和其他 Garmin 手表最多可节省 270 美元</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;绿色背包上的 Fenix 7S Pro&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/HXB7-LURlTvA90BgnaHKSKYzcBo=/0x0:2550x1700/1310x873/cdn. vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73723786/236729_Garmin_Fenix_7S_Pro_AKrales_0127.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;很难找到一款能像 Fenix 7 Pro 系列那样追踪如此多的锻炼和指标的健身手表。&lt;/em>; |摄影：Amelia Holowaty Krales / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;SQdYAd&quot;>;Garmin 制造了一些最好的传统多运动健身手表，其一款顶级型号仍然在我们的最佳手表列表中占有一席之地。 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/22985108/best-fitness-tracker&quot;>;最佳健身追踪器&lt;/a>;：&lt;strong>;Garmin Fenix 7S Pro。现在，通过“网络星期一”，您只需 529.99 美元（折扣 270 美元）即可在 &lt;a href=&quot;https://go.redirectingat.com?id=66960X1514734&amp;amp;xs=1&amp;amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wellbots.com%2Fproducts%2Fgarmin-fenix-7s-pro-solar-smartwatch&amp;amp; ;referrer=theverge.com&amp;amp;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2024%2F11%2F14%2F24296364%2Fgarmin-fenix-7s-pro-forerunner-265-inreach-mini-2-deal-sale ”使用 &lt;em>;Verge&lt;/em>; 专有代码 &lt;strong>;VERGEBF270&lt;/strong>; 时，rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;Wellbots&lt;/a>;。该代码也适用于基础版 Fenix 7 Pro（&lt;a href=&quot;https://go.redirectingat.com?id=66960X1514734&amp;amp;xs=1&amp;amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wellbots.com%2Fproducts%2Fgarmin-fenix-7-pro-solar-smartwatch&amp;amp; ;referrer=theverge.com&amp;amp;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2024%2F11%2F14%2F24296364%2Fgarmin-fenix-7s-pro-forerunner-265-inreach-mini-2-deal-sale ” rel=&quot; Sponsored nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;折扣后 529.99 美元&lt;/a>;），Fenix 7X Pro（&lt;